        "Hi, Jane.",
        "How are you? I hope you\u2019re doing well. I am writing to you to ask for advice about my future job interview.",
        "I told you before that I had a problem at work. My boss didn\u2019t promote me at 2 years and yesterday I asked him directly about it and he declined. This is the reason why I decided to quit my job.",
